'''''Hook's Treasure''''' is a [[Companion Mission]] in the chapter [[Slices of Life Before the Furnace]].

==Steps==
# Ask Hook what she wants from you
# Meet Hook at Rivet Town
# Find the other treasure in the orphanage
# Use Findie to find the hidden treasure
# Find the treasure Julian needs
# Use Findie to find the hidden treasure
# Return to the clinic and ask Natasha to fix the doll
# Help Hook find her treasure
# Protect Hook and defeat the monsters in the orphanage
# Return to the clinic and ask Natasha to fix the doll

